(7, 'Please-Help-Yuvaan-Ramtekkar-Get-The-World\'s-Costliest-Drug!20210403093406.jpg', '180000000', '180000000', 'Please help Yuvaan Ramtekkar get the world\'s costliest drug!', 'Help Baby Yuvaan Fight Spinal Muscular Atrophy ', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Yuvaan suffers from Spinal Muscular Atrophy and has difficulty holding his neck, trying to breathe, swallow, and moving his legs like any other infant of his age.</span><strong> </strong>Zolgensma Gene Therapy is a potential cure for SMA for children, and it has to be imported from the USA. Baby Yuvaan needs Zolgensma gene therapy as soon as possible to save his life. Zolgensma comes at an extortionate price of INR 15&ndash;18 crores, approximately, excluding taxes and duties.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Yuvaan&#39;s father works for a company and earns around INR 27,000 per month. Until now, his treatments and medications have been paid for with savings and loans. But the price of Zolgensma gene therapy is beyond their reach. They are unable to afford the medical treatment for their baby boy, whom they love so much.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">We sincerely appeal to the Helping Hearts like you to come forward and extend your full support to enable us to help Yuvaan. We request that you kindly contribute towards the treatment by sending your contribution by Cheque/DD/Online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha and help during this time of desperate need. Each contribution is significant, irrespective of the amount.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2', '2022-10-13 12:24:26'),
(8, 'Your-support-will-help-Daily-wage-worker-to-treat-his-Son.20200801104455_1.jpg', '250000', '250000', 'Your Support Will Help a Father Treat His Son.', 'Your help is the only chance for baby Rudra to survive', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Child Rudra is fighting against heart disease at Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">We humbly request you to help Rudra, who is suffering from congenital heart disease, as certified by the doctors and is being treated at Jerbai Wadia Hospital, Mumbai (OP No.3077798). Rudra needs to undergo open heart surgery. Due to their financial condition, they could not operate Rudra. His health started deteriorating day by day, so they took him to Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital for Children. The doctors informed them that they need to admit Rudra and start his surgery process. It is a long-term treatment that will cost around Rs. 2,50,000/-.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Rudra&#39;s father is a daily wage worker and earns approx. INR 7000 per month. But due to COVID-19, he is at home fighting for his son and his family without any source of income. He is fighting for the daily needs and treatment of a 3 month old suffering from heart disease. They are unable to afford the medical treatment for their son, whom they love so much.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">As a result, we humbly request that you come forward and lend us your full support so that we can treat Rudra.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">The operation is estimated to cost Rs. 2,50,000/-. We appeal to YOU to save a life by sending your contribution by cheque/DD/Online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha at the address given below.</span></span></p>\r\n', '2', '2022-10-13 12:30:22'),
(9, 'My-Son-is-battling-blood-cancer-help_1.webp', '225000', '1500000', 'My Son Is Battling Blood Cancer, help me to save his life.', 'Please do not let death take my son.', '<p>A father&rsquo;s plea: My son does not understand what cancer is and how it is affecting him, but I do! Vikrant started battling thalassemia when he was only 4 months old. It is so heart-pricking to see him suffer at this young age. We have seen him suffer enough and we can&rsquo;t take it anymore. I am the only breadwinner in my family, which consists of four members, and my earnings can barely feed them. I have put all my savings and earnings towards my son&rsquo;s treatment. I have knocked on many doors for help. We can&rsquo;t imagine losing our child. Vikrant has to undergo monthly blood transfusions. My son is losing his life and your support can save him.<br><br>We need Rs 15,00,000 (fifteen lakhs) for his allogeneic bone marrow transplant. We are unable to pay for his treatment because we can&rsquo;t afford such a large amount. I request you to contribute towards the treatment and help in this hour of need.<br><br>Each contribution is important! Please help with the required amount and save my child.<br><br>We are grateful for your help and good wishes.</p>', '1', '2022-10-31 18:03:50'),
(10, 'soham.webp', '520000', '650000', 'Soham’s Mother Needs Him Let’s Save His Life.', 'There’s always hope beyond what we see, so let’s support Soham to fight cancer with courage.', '<p>Mother&rsquo;s Plea: My name is Archana Shinde, and I am based in Aurangabad, Maharashtra. My son, Soham, is just 7 years old. My son is the apple of my eyes, but right now he is spending his toddler age with this dreadful disease of acute lymphoblastic leukemia cancer. We work as daily wage workers on a farm, earning 5000/- per month while trying to balance food and expenses. Even if we worked day and night, we wouldn&rsquo;t be able to afford his treatment.<br><br>My child is confined between four walls, Cancer took his childhood away. Only your support can give him a better life and the opportunities for a bright future.<br><br>I request you to come forward and support him as his life-saving treatment costs 6,50,000/-Help us to secure his life. Only your contribution will add value to his life.<br><br>The approximate cost for the procedure is Rs. 6,50,000/- (6 Lakhs, 50 Thousands Only) . Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online Online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</p>', '1', '2022-10-31 18:46:15'),
(11, 'Lets-be-a-light-of-hope-and-help-Manas-win-his-chronicle-cancer-affray20210603060157-1-370x410.webp', '350000', '1000000', ' Let’s Be A Light Of Hope And Help Manas Win His Chronicle Cancer Affray.', 'Manas is the only beacon of hope for his parents. Let’s save him from cancer.', '<p>We humbly request that you assist Master Manas, an 11-year-old boy suffering from cancer (Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia) and being treated at Kamalnayan Bajaj Hospital. Master Manas is 11 years old and needs intensive chemotherapy and bone marrow transplants. Due to their financial condition, they could not operate Manas. His health started deteriorating day by day, so they took him to Kamalnayan Bajaj Hospital. The doctors informed them that he needed to be admitted to Manas and needed to start urgent chemotherapy and bone marrow transplants. It is a long-term treatment with an approximate expenditure of 10,00,000.<br><br>His father works as an office boy and earns 8000/-per month, and his mother is a housewife. Since the entire family and his parents are dependent on him, he is naturally not in a position to bear the cost of the treatment of Master Manas.<br><br>As a result, we humbly request that Helping Hearts like YOU come forward and lend us your full support in order for us to treat Master Manas. Please join hands in our mission to save the precious life of Master Manas and donate generously. Your contribution is very valuable to enabling the child to survive.<br><br>The operation is estimated to cost Rs. 10,00,000/-. We appeal to YOU to save the life of Master Manas by sending your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</p>', '1', '2022-10-31 18:53:17'),
(12, 'Be-a-ray-of-hope-for-Sanaya-and-help-her-to-battle-hepatoblastoma-High-Risk20210810035457-2.webp', '300000', '500000', 'Be A Ray Of Hope For Sanaya And Help Her Battle Hepatoblastoma.', 'A one-year-old little soul is battling hepatoblastoma and all she needs is your support for a miracle to happen.', '<p>Sanaya has been diagnosed with hepatoblastoma and requires IPD/OPD treatment for approximately 8 months. She has to undergo chemotherapy and surgery, and the estimated cost of her treatment is Rs. 5,00,000, which includes investigation, medicine, surgery, specific procedure, bed charges, and supportive therapy. Her prognosis is moderately good. We implore you to help Sanaya in this battle by donating however much you can.<br><br>Her father, Sultan Shaikh, is the sole breadwinner, and her mother, Fatima, is a housewife. Sanaya has a 5-year-old sister named Anshara. Her father is a small shopkeeper, and both her parents have a locomotor disability. Sanaya hails from a small village named Beed in Maharashtra. Initially, her parents noticed a lump on her belly and took her to the nearby hospital, where she was diagnosed with liver cancer. The doctor informed them to take her to Pune or Mumbai for treatment, and the family managed to get her admitted to Bharati Hospital for further treatment and chemotherapy. She has undergone five chemotherapies. A doctor has informed the family that Sanaya might have to undergo a liver transplant or else surgery. The treatment is estimated to cost Rs. 5,00,000/- (five lakhs only).<br><br>We sincerely ask helping hearts like YOU to come forward and lend your full support in this desperate situation so that Baby Sanaya can receive the necessary treatment, save her precious life, and help this little soul live. Each and every contribution of yours is valuable to enable the child to survive. Please be a part of our mission and donate.<br><br>The approximate cost for the operation is Rs. 5,00,000. Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</p>', '1', '2022-10-31 18:59:59'),
(13, '9.jpg', '84000', '420000', 'Saloni Needs Your Support For Neuro Regenerative Rehabilitation Therapy.', 'COVID has taken away the breadwinner of the family, Now the family can’t digest losing their child.', '<p>Saloni has been diagnosed with Rett Syndrome. She has been recommended for Neuro Regenerative Rehabilitation therapy. The treatment involves a 14-day hospital stay, during which time she will be extensively evaluated clinically. This will be followed by a bone marrow aspiration from which, subsequently, the mononuclear cells will be isolated. These are hematopoietic mononuclear cells which are injected intrathecally through a lumbar puncture and CSF catheter. This is followed by 4 days of intensive physiotherapy, occupational therapy, speech therapy, counselling, and other medical treatment as required.<br><br>Saloni is 7 years old and lives in Kolhapur, Maharashtra. She led a normal life till she was 2 years old. One night, unfortunately, she got a high fever and was admitted to the hospital. She did not get well; she was not able to get up, understand anything, eat, go to the washroom, and do her regular activities. The doctor suggested her to undergo treatment and therapies. The family is too poor to bear the expense of the treatment. Her father, Mr. Prajot, passed away due to COVID and her mother, Mrs. Vidya, is a housewife. Saloni has a younger sister named Rudra, who is 3 years old. Now the whole burden and expenses of this family is taken care of by her uncle, who works in a garage as a daily wage labourer. Saloni needs your support to manage her rare disease.<br><br>We implore generous hearts like you to come forward and extend your fullest support in this heart-pricking situation for Saloni&rsquo;s family to make it possible for her to undergo treatment and therapies. Each and every contribution of yours will help her get better and manage her rare disease.&nbsp;<br><br>The approximate cost for the procedure is Rs.4,20,000/-&nbsp; (Four lakhs twenty&nbsp; thousand only) Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</p>', '1', '2022-10-31 19:16:25'),
(14, 'Our-drive-is-to-support-six-year-old-Ganesh-who-is-suffering-from-Thalassemia20210917030828-1-370x410.webp', '50000', '500000', 'Our Goal Is To Support Six-Year Old Ganesh, Who Is Suffering From Thalassemia.', 'Ganesh is in ICU suffering from Thalassemia, Your generous effort will help to give him a new life.', '<div class=\"elementor-column-gap-default elementor-container\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-col-100 elementor-column elementor-element elementor-element-6b083d7 elementor-top-column\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-element-populated elementor-widget-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-48d1ada elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">Ganesh has been diagnosed with thalassemia. He has been advised to have chemotherapy and supportive care. The expense of the treatment includes chemotherapy, medicine investigation, test charges, hospital charges, and drug charges.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGanesh hails from Nashik, Maharashtra. His father, Mr. Prabhakar, is the sole bread earner in the family. He works in a small company and earns 20,000 per month. His mother is a housewife and has a sister who is 13 years old. This havoc has damaged the family financially and emotionally. They are not able to bear the expense of the treatment. The family has been knocking on doors to pay the expenses of the treatment.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe are requesting you to show your compassion and contribute to Ganesh&rsquo;s treatment. Make it possible for him to get the treatment at the right time and save his life. Each and every contribution of yours will give him a chance to increase his survival. We, together, can bring this family back from this devastating situation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe procedure is estimated to cost Rs. 5,00,000/- (five lakhs only). Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"elementor-column-gap-default elementor-container\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-col-100 elementor-column elementor-element elementor-element-c58d81d elementor-top-column\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-element-populated elementor-widget-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b2b8870 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '1', '2022-10-31 19:21:59'),
(15, 'Lets-give-a-chance-to-Zohan-today-to-relive-a-better-life-tomorrow.20211207073918-370x410.jpg', '195000', '650000', ' Let’s Give A Chance To Zohan Today To Relive A Better Life Tomorrow.', 'Cancer has already affected his academic year, and now it is trying to ruin his future', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">CASE STUDY: Zohanuddin, a 6-month-old boy, has been battling Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia. Prior to that, he had been living a very normal life with his friends and family. All of a sudden, his middle childhood was hit by a chronic disease, cancer.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Zohan and his family belong to Jalgaon. His mother is a housewife and his father, Riyazuddin, was an electrician who is now jobless as they have left everything behind and, in hope, arrived in Aurangabad only for their little child&rsquo;s treatment. They have put all their savings and borrowed money from friends and relatives to cure this deadly illness that happened to their son.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Dear donors, we humbly request you to come forward and extend your full support, which can enable us to treat child Zohan and save him from this atrocious malady. Your contribution can add value to his treatment.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">The approximate cost for the procedure is Rs. 6,50,000/-(6 Lakhs, 50 Thousands Only). Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '1', '2022-10-31 19:26:50'),
(16, 'He-just-started-to-see-the-world-but-cancer-is-not-even-giving-him-a-chance-to-survive.-20220128051306.jpg', '40000', '200000', ' He Just Started To See The World, But Cancer Is Not Even Giving Him A Chance To Survive.', 'His cancer is spreading rapidly, but this little toddler is looking for your support.', '<p>A father&rsquo;s plea : Our son&rsquo;s birth has given our life a new meaning; with his little hands and sweet smiles, our days were always brighter. He is our world and seeing him in pain is unbearable for us. My son Rahil is only two and a half years old. It was during the month of November 2021 that he started developing a high fever and had a lump on his right eye. Then we followed the medical treatment as suggested by the doctor. But there was no improvement in his condition. Further, as suggested after multiple investigations, he was diagnosed with &ldquo;Retinoblastoma&rdquo; (a type of eye cancer which spreads beyond the eye to other parts), for which the only curative treatment is worth about Rs. 2,00,000/-approx. that includes hospitalization, chemotherapy, investigation, and procedures with antibiotics and medical products. I am working as a house painter and my income is not enough to bear the expense of Rahil&rsquo;s treatment. All our savings, with borrowed funds and multiple loans, have been spent on the treatment so far. Now there is no option left with us to arrange this hefty sum. Months have passed since I last saw my son struggling with life in such a miserable condition. With a life ahead of him, he shouldn&rsquo;t be at the receiving end of such a fatal disease. It breaks my heart to see him crying for help. I stand helpless, as there is nothing more I can do for him. All my son needs is a helping hand, which will go a long way towards saving his life.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYour kindness will give this baby a new life.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe approximate cost for the procedure is Rs. 2,00,000/-(2 lakhs only). Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</p>\r\n', '1', '2022-10-31 19:31:11'),
(17, 'Lets-help-Shravani-to-fight-against-lymphomawhichiIs-a-very-rare-but-aggressive-cancer20201010113309-1-370x410.webp', '250000', '500000', 'Lets Help Shravani To Fight Against Leukemia, Which Is A Very Rare But Aggressive Cancer.', 'Help baby Shravani fight against b-cell all (acute lymphoblastic leukemia, a type of blood cancer).', '<p>We humbly request you to help Baby Shravani Ahire, who is suffering from B CELL ALL (acute lymphoblastic leukaemia, a type of blood cancer); it&rsquo;s a rare cancer. She is being admitted to the HCG Manavata Cancer Centre in Nashik. Due to poor financial conditions, they could not treat Baby Shravani. Doctors informed them that they needed to undergo treatment for B-cell all (acute lymphoblastic leukaemia, a type of blood cancer). It is a long-term treatment with an estimated cost of Rs. 5,00,000/-family.<br><br>Her father is a daily wage earner from a village near Nashik, Maharashtra. Her father earned Rs. 6000/-per month for their survival, but now due to the pandemic, he is unemployed. Her family is not in a position to make funding arrangements for the child&rsquo;s treatment. We, therefore, sincerely appeal to the Helping Hands like YOU to come forward and extend your full support to enable us to treat baby Shravani.<br><br>Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</p>', '1', '2022-10-31 19:37:54'),
(18, 'Cancer-is-crushing-Ishwaris-childhood-e1651046586.jpg', '300000', '600000', 'Cancer Is Crushing Ishwari’s Childhood', 'Ishwari is just 3 years old and does not deserve to endure such hardships.', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Ishwari toddles around like any other curious three-year-old who has just discovered playing and running. But sadly for her, the fun doesn&rsquo;t last long. She was just 3 years old, unaware of the reality, wailing in pain.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">In reality, it is the cancer that hinders her life.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Mother&rsquo;s plea, &quot;When Ishwari was born, our whole family was in celebration. She is our first child. But our happiness was short-lived. I remember that day five months ago when she started crying in the middle of the night. We couldn&rsquo;t pacify her. At that very moment, I knew that if we didn&rsquo;t take her to the hospital in time, we would lose her. &quot; </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Ishwari&rsquo;s father is a fisherman, whose income is never fixed. His family struggles for daily bread and cannot borrow such a huge amount.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Their only hope is their child. Hence, come forward and extend your generous support. Please be a miracle in their lives and save our only daughter from cancer. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">The procedure is expected to cost Rs. 6,00,000/- (Rs. Six Lakh Only). Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1', '2022-10-31 19:45:33'),
(19, 'Help-Mast-Manthan-fight-Cancer-in-this-challenging-situation-of-Pandemic20210508030044-1-e1651467478702.webp', '280000', '700000', 'Help Mast Manthan Fight Cancer In This Challenging Situation Of Pandemic', 'Manthan is fighting two viruses simultaneously: cancer in his body and Corona outside!!! Only you can give him victory.', '<p>Manthan is fighting two viruses simultaneously: cancer in his body and Corona outside!!! Only you can give him victory.<br><br>We humbly request that you help 7-year-old Mast Manthan, who is suffering from cancer (Acute Lymphoblastic Leukaemia) and is being treated at Surya Mother &amp; Child Care Hospital. Mast Manthan is 7 years old and needs to undergo 6 intensive chemotherapy sessions. Due to the family&rsquo;s financial condition, they could not operate Manthan. They took him to Surya Mother &amp; Child Care Hospital after his health kept deteriorating, and the doctors informed them that the child had cancer and must undergo chemotherapy immediately. It is a long-term treatment that will cost approximately Rs. 7,00,000/-.<br><br>His father works in a private company and earns Rs. 9,000/-per month, and his mother is a housewife. The financial condition is the biggest barrier to this innocent child&rsquo;s ability to fight cancer.<br><br is=\"\">&nbsp;The approximate cost of the operation is Rs. 70,0000/-. We appeal to you to save the life of Master Manthan by sending your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</p>', '1', '2022-10-31 19:50:33'),
(20, 'Help-Master-Anuj20191115101139.webp', '235000', '235000', 'Anuj needs your help to overcome heart disease', 'Your contribution can go a long way in helping a child fight for their life..!!!', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">We humbly request you to help 6.5-year-old Anuj, who is suffering from heart disease. The poor financial situation of his family prevented him from having surgery, which led to his health deteriorating rapidly. Balaji Heart Hospital &amp; Diagnostic Centre doctors informed them that he needs to undergo an urgent heart surgery. It is a major open heart surgery with an approximate cost of 2,35,000/- </span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">His father is a daily wage worker and his&nbsp; mother is a housewife.&nbsp; As a result of their financial situation, they could not afford to treat him.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">We, therefore, sincerely appeal to the Helping Hearts like YOU to come forward and extend your full support to enable us to treat this child. Please join hands in our mission for this cause of saving the precious life of Anuj and donate generously. Your contribution is very valuable to enable the child to survive.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">The approximate cost for the operation is Rs. 2,35,000/- for an Open Heart Surgery. We appeal to YOU to save the life of Anuj by sending your contribution by Cheque/DD/Online in the name of Kokan Sanstha at the address given below.</span></span></span></p>\r\n', '2', '2022-10-31 20:11:55'),
(21, 'Help-Baby-Bhakti-to-Save-Her-Life20191117113800.webp', '225000', '225000', ' Help Baby Bhakti by saving her life.', 'Help 6-years old baby girl Bhakti, who is suffering from heart disease.', '<p>We humbly request you to help six-year-old baby girl Bhakti, who is suffering from heart disease. Due to their financial condition, they could not operate her and as a result, her health started deteriorating day by day. The Balaji Heart Hospital &amp; Diagnostic Centre&rsquo;s doctors informed them that she needed to undergo heart surgery. It is a major open heart surgery with an estimated cost of Rs. 225,000/-.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHer father is a daily wage worker, and her mother is a housewife. Her father earns Rs. 4000&ndash;5000/-per month, and is unable to bear the cost of the treatment of Bhakti.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs a result, we humbly request that helping hearts like you come forward and extend your full support so that we can treat this child. Please join hands in our mission to save the precious life of Baby Bhakti and donate generously.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYour contribution is very valuable to enabling the child to survive. The approximate cost of the operation is Rs. 2,25,000/-for an open heart surgery. We appeal to YOU to save the life of Baby Bhakti by sending your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Sanstha at the address given below.</p>\r\n', '2', '2022-10-31 20:16:03'),
(22, 'Help-baby-boy-Shreel-Naik-who-is-suffering-from-Cancer20191118120231.webp', '400000', '400000', 'Help Baby Boy Shreel Naik, Who Is Suffering From Cancer.', 'Your support will help 8-months old Shreel who is suffering from cancer.', '<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>We humbly request you to help 8-months old Shreel, who is suffering from an acute Leukaemia, a type of blood cancer and is being treated at Wadia Hospital. His health started deteriorating day by day, so they took him to Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital for Children. The doctors informed them that the baby has cancer and needs to be admitted to start an urgent chemotherapy. It is a long-term treatment that will cost around 400,000/-.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>His father is working in a private company and earns 8000/-per month, and his mother is a housewife. Due to their financial condition, they could not provide treatment for him.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>As a result, we humbly request that Helping Hearts like YOU come forward and lend us your full support so that we can treat Shreel. Please join hands in our mission to save the precious life of Shreel and donate generously. Your contribution is very valuable to enabling the child to survive. We appeal to YOU to save the life of Shreel by sending your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2', '2022-10-31 20:20:48'),
(23, 'Help-Master-Rudra20191205092107.webp', '400000', '400000', 'Help little Rudra Misal fight cancer.', 'The only thing that can save his life is your blessing and support.', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#262626\">We humbly request you to help Rudra, who is suffering from cancer (acute leukaemia) and is being treated in Wadia Hospital, Mumbai. Rudra Misal is 2 years old and needs to undergo chemotherapy. Due to their financial condition, they could not operate Rudra. His health started deteriorating day by day, so they took him to Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital for Children. The doctors informed them that he needs to be admitted to Rudra to begin with urgent chemotherapy. It is a long-term treatment that will cost approximately Rs. 400, 000/-</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#262626\">His father is working as a labourer and earns Rs. 3500/-per month, and his mother is a housewife. Since the entire family is dependent on him, he is&nbsp; not in a position to bear the cost of the treatment of Rudra.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#262626\">We therefore, sincerely appeal to the helping Hearts like you to come forward and extend your full support to enable us to treat Rudra. Please join hands in our mission to save the precious life ofRudra and donate generously. Your contribution is very valuable to enabling the child to survive.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#262626\">The operation is estimated to cost Rs. 400,000/-. We appeal to YOU to save the life of Rudra by sending your contribution by c