(24, 'Help-angel-Muskan-to-save-Her-Life20191213012703.webp', '270000', '270000', 'Help Angel Muskan To Save Her Life', 'Baby Muskan, 2 years old, is suffering from heart disease. Your support can put a smile on her parents’ faces.', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#404040\">We humbly request that you help 2-year-old Baby Girl Muskan, who is suffering from heart disease. Due to their financial condition, they could not operate her and her health started deteriorating day by day. The Balaji Heart Hospital &amp; Diagnostic Centre&#39;s doctors informed them she needs to undergo an urgent heart surgery. It is a major open heart surgery with an approximate cost of 270,000/-</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#404040\">Her father is a daily wage worker, and her mother is a housewife. Her father earns Rs. 3000&ndash;4000/-per month. Since he is the only breadwinner of the family, he is not in a position to bear the cost of the treatment of baby Muskan.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#404040\">&nbsp;We therefore, sincerely appeal to the Helping Hearts like YOU to come forward and extend your full support to enable us to treat this child. Please join hands in our mission to save the precious life of Baby Muskan and donate generously. Your contribution is very valuable to enabling the child to survive.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p 