(33, '12success-370x400.jpg', '220000', '220000', '2 years old Adarsh needs help for her open heart surgery', 'Give baby Adarsh a fighting chance against heart disease', '<p>We humbly request you to help Adarsh, who is suffering from congenital heart disease, as certified by the doctors and is being treated at Jerbai Wadia Hospital, Mumbai. Adarsh needs to undergo open heart surgery. Due to their financial condition, they could not operate Adarsh. His health started deteriorating day by day, so they took him to Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital for Children. The doctors informed them that they needed to admit Adarsh to start his surgery process. It is a long-term treatment with an estimated cost of Rs. 2,20,000/-family.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAdarsh&rsquo;s father works as a security guard and earns approximately INR 9000 per month. He is fighting for the daily needs and treatment of his 2-year-old baby boy suffering from heart disease. They are unable to afford the medical treatment for their baby boy, whom they love so much.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe, sincerely appeal to the Helping Hearts like you to come forward and extend your full support to enable us to treat Adarsh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe operation is estimated to cost Rs. 2,20,000/- We appeal to you to save the life of Adarsh by sending your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha at the address given below.</p>\r\n', '2', '2022-10-31 21:00:05'),
