(35, 'KEDAR PHOTO.jpeg', '10000', '800000', 'My child is fighting for his life; please help him.', 'It breaks my heart to see him helplessly cry in pain.', '<p>Child Kedar is only 12 years old and battling blood cancer at such a young age. He is being admitted to the MGM Medical Hospital, Aurangabad. Doctors informed us that they needed to undergo Chemotherapy treatment for B-cell (Acute myeloid leukaemia, a type of blood cancer). It is a long-term treatment that is expected to cost Rs. 8,00,000/-.</p>\r\n<p>Kedar has been undergoing unimaginable pain and trauma.The endless treatment cycles and their effects on the child have left the family emotionally and financially exhausted. The expenses are huge, and they have already put everything at risk, but now they have no resources to pay for their child&rsquo;s life-threatening, expensive treatment.</p>\r\n<p>We request that you kindly contribute towards the treatment and help during this time of desperate need. Each contribution is significant, irrespective of the amount. Helping Kedar would contribute to his recovery and help him look forward to a healthy life. Please send your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2022-11-18 10:17:38'),
(36, 'He-spent-a-decade-of-his-life-battling-cancer.-Only-you-can-change-his-future.20220503060222.jpg', '750000', '1500000', 'He spent a decade of his life battling cancer. Only you can change his future.', 'Hope is the final word for his bright future ahead, and you can make a difference.', '<p style=\"margin-left:-15px; margin-right:-15px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Yash was just 2 years old when he first faced the miserable pain of Cancer. He often complains of pain in different parts of his body, way too little to express his uneasiness. I am ready to sacrifice my own life for my son. I am his mother and am willing to do anything to protect him. My only fault is that I am unable to pay for his treatment due to our family&rsquo;s poor conditions. My husband, Bharat, owns a small shop and an eatery from home. He hardly earns 500 in a day. We took loans at interest to fund our son. It&rsquo;s been 10 long years since we&#39;ve been struggling just to see him healthy, but CANCER doesn&rsquo;t let him live.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:-15px; margin-right:-15px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">Their only hope is that their child suffering from cancer will find help. Hence, come forward and extend your generous support. Each and every contribution of yours will give him a chance to increase his survival.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:-15px; margin-right:-15px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\">The approximate cost for the procedure is Rs. 15,00,000/- (Fifteen Lakhs Only). Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of <strong>Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1', '2022-11-29 10:24:26'),
(37, 'Mast.-Aryan-10-Month-old-Warrior-Need-Your-Support-to-Fight-his-Heart-Battle20201117053158.jpg', '250000', '250000', 'Aryan is just a 10 month old warrior and needs your support to fight his heart battle.', 'Let us be the light of hope for Aryan Joshi and save his life.', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">We humbly request you to help Aryan, who is suffering from congenital heart disease, as certified by the doctors and is being treated at Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital for Children, Mumbai. Aryan needs to </span></span></span><strong>undergo open heart surgery (Arterial Switch Operation).</strong> Due to their financial condition, they could not operate&nbsp; Aryan. His health started deteriorating day by day, so they took him to Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital for Children. The doctors informed them that they need to admit Aryan and start his surgery process. It is a long-term treatment that will cost approximately Rs.2,50,000/-</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Aryan&#39;s father is </span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffefef\">working as a </span>&nbsp;part-time watchman and earns approx. INR 7,800 per month. But due to COVID-19, he is at home fighting for his son and his family without any source of income. He is fighting for the daily needs and treatment of his 10-month old baby boy suffering from heart disease. They are unable to afford the medical treatment for their baby boy, whom they love so much.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">As a result, we humbly request that you come forward and lend us your full support in order for us to treat Aryan.</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The operation is estimated to cost Rs. 2,50,000/-. We appeal to YOU to save the life of Aryan by sending your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of </span></span></span><strong>Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha </strong>at the address given below.</span></span></p>\r\n', '2', '2022-11-29 17:05:48'),
(38, 'Baby-Yasdnya-wants-to-live…-can-you-save-this-little-angel-!!!20201121073446.jpg', '200000', '200000', 'Baby Yadnya Wants To Live... Can You Save This Little Angel!', 'Your support will help her parent to give her new life', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">We humbly request your help to help Baby Yadnya, who is suffering from congenital heart disease, as certified by the doctors and is being treated at Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital for Children, Mumbai. Baby Yadnya needs to undergo open heart surgery (VSD Closure). Due to their financial condition, they could not operate Baby Yadnya. Her health started deteriorating day by day, so they took him to Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital for Children&rsquo;s. The doctors informed them that they need to admit Yadnya and start her surgery process. It is a long-term treatment that will cost approximately Rs. 2,00,000/-.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yadnya&#39;s father is working as a counter salesman in a shop and earns approximately INR. 7,500 per month. But due to COVID-19, he is at home fighting for the survival of his baby and his family without any source of income. He is fighting for the daily needs and treatment of his 2-month-old baby girl suffering from heart disease. They are unable to afford the medical treatment for their baby girl, whom they love so much.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">As a result, we humbly request that you come forward and lend us your full support so that we can treat Baby Yadnya.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The approximate cost for the operation is Rs. 2,00,000/-. We appeal to you to save the life of Baby Yadnya by sending your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha at the address given below. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2', '2022-11-29 17:17:02'),
(39, 'Mast-Joel-Has-a-bleeding-Heart-can-you-help-in-mend-it-for-his-long-awaiting-parent.20210202034921.jpg', '200000', '200000', 'Joel Has A Bleeding Heart Can You Help Him Mend It For His Long Awaiting Parents', 'Save Joel from a heart defect to bring new hope to his wailing parents.', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">We humbly request you to help Joel, who is suffering from congenital heart disease, as certified by the doctors and is being treated in Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital for Children, Mumbai. Joel needs to undergo open heart surgery (VSD Closure + DCRV Relief). Due to their financial condition, they could not operate&nbsp; Joel. His health started deteriorating day by day, so they took him to Bai Jerbai Wadia Hospital for Children. The doctors informed them that they need to admit Joel and start his surgery process. It is a long-term treatment that will cost approximately Rs. 2,00,000/-.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The father of Joel is working as an assistant lightman and earns approx. INR.7,800 per month. But due to COVID-19, he is at home fighting for his son and his family without any source of income. He is fighting for the daily needs and treatment of his 11-month old baby boy suffering from heart disease. They are unable to afford the medical treatment for their baby boy, whom they love so much.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">We, therefore, sincerely appeal to the Helping Hearts like YOU to come forward and extend your full support to enable us to treat. Joel.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The approximate cost for the operation is Rs. 2,00,000/-. We appeal to YOU to save the life of Joel by sending your contribution by cheque/DD/Online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2', '2022-11-29 17:32:37'),
(40, 'Before-we-say-Educate-Girl-Child,-We-Must-Save-Girls20210309022720.JPG', '250000', '250000', 'Before We Educate a Girl Child, We Must Save A Girl !', 'Let’s save a girl child who can become the pride of our nation.', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">We humbly request you to help Baby Aaradhya, who is suffering from congenital heart disease and is being treated at Balaji Heart Hospital &amp; Diagnostic Center, Mumbai. Baby Aaradhya needs to undergo an open heart surgery (ICR of ASD Closure). Due to their financial condition, they could not operate Baby Aaradhya. Her health started deteriorating day by day, so they took her to Balaji Heart Hospital &amp; Diagnostic Center. The doctors informed them that they needed to admit Aaradhya and start her surgery process. This is a long-term treatment that will cost approximately Rs. 2,50,000/-.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Aradhya&#39;s father is a farmer who is going through a tough phase due to disasters. He </span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffefef\">is</span> searching for livelihood, and his daughter&#39;s heart disease is the worst nightmare for the family.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;As a result, we humbly request that you come forward and lend us your full support so that we can treat Baby Aaradhya.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The operation is estimated to cost Rs. 2,50,000/-. We appeal to you to save the life of Baby Aaradhya by sending your contribution by cheque/DD/Online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '2', '2022-11-29 17:37:55'),
(41, 'One-year-old-Shreyas-wants-your-support-to-undergo-Open-Heart-Surgery20210918112008.JPG', '303000', '303000', 'One-Year Old Shreyas Wants Your Support To Undergo Open Heart Surgery', 'Little toddler is looking up to you for your support, envision your role and give a life to Shreyas. ', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Shreyas is just 1 year and 6 months old. He hails from Ahmednagar, Maharashtra. He is diagnosed with Double outlet right ventricle with severe PS. He has to undergo repair of DORV (Complex opasen heart surgery) Please make it possible for him to win this surgery and survive by contributing as much as possible.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Family Scenario: Shreyas hails from Ahmednagar, Maharashtra. There are 4 members in his family. His father&rsquo;s name is Sunil, who works as a daily wage labour and his mother, Shubhangi, is a housewife and an elder sister, Deepali, who is 3 years old. Shreyas was diagnosed with heart disease and admitted to Baramati Hospital. For further treatment, the doctor recommended the parents to shift him to Jupiter Hospital, Pune. Kindly show your generous heart to support this child and help him survive.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">We implore you to envision your role and contribute generously to Shreyas. His father is very poor, and with much difficulty he earns his daily bread. Unfortunately the child is suffering from heart disease. The family can&rsquo;t imagine losing their child. Help Shreyas to undergo surgery and make it possible for him to survive and lead a normal life. Each and every contribution of yours will give him a hope of survival.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The approximate cost for the procedure is Rs.3,03,000/-(Three lakhs three thousand only). Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '2', '2022-11-29 17:40:40'),
(42, 'You-are-the-last-hope-of-helping-him-win-the-battle-against-blood-cancer.20220608065334.jpg', '315000', '650000', 'You are the last hope of helping him win the battle against blood cancer.', 'Cancer has robbed our little boy’s childhood and he is suffering tremendously!', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Sarwadnya is only 5 years old and already battling blood cancer at such a young age. Cancer has ruined his childhood, affecting his academic performance and turning his life upside down.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Sarwadnya and his family belong to Mudkhed village in Nanded district, and his parents work on a farm as daily wage earners. It&#39;s not been easy for them to deal with everything their son is going through, and their financial situation has made it difficult to provide him with treatments such as lumbar punctures, bone marrow operations, blood transfusions, and chemotherapy.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Dear donors, your prayers and contributions can make a difference in Sarwadnya&rsquo;s life. Cancer isn&rsquo;t the end, but for those who can&rsquo;t afford treatment, it can be. With your support, a child facing a fatal disease can get the help they need, so let&rsquo;s come together to help save a valuable life.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Your contribution will go a long way in ensuring a happy and healthy life for children with cancer and their families. Let&rsquo;s give a chance to Sarwadnya today, to relive a better life tomorrow.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">The approximate cost for the procedure is Rs. 6,50,000/-(6 Lakhs, 50 Thousand Only). Send a contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1', '2022-11-29 17:59:06'),
(43, 'Mariya\'s-cancer-will-take-her-life.20220722041357.jpg', '250000', '650000', 'Mariya\'s cancer will take her life.', 'Cancer already stole her childhood; don’t let it steal her life.', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:-15px; margin-right:-15px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Our family&#39;s happiness lies in Mariya. She is suffering from cancer is the worst news our family could ever receive. She is being admitted to the Mahatma Gandhi Cancer Hospital and Research Institute, Aurangabad. Doctors informed us that they needed to undergo treatment for B-cell all (acute lymphoblastic leukemia, a type of blood cancer). It is a long-term treatment that is expected to cost Rs. 6,50,000/-.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:-15px; margin-right:-15px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">We are doing everything possible to save our daughter. Mariya has been a warrior so far, and she deserves your help to live a normal, healthy life. She is spending much of her childhood getting poked by needles, giving blood, sleeping in hospital beds, and receiving harsh chemotherapy. The expenses are huge, and we have already put everything we own at risk to save our little daughter, But now, we have no resources to pay for her life-saving, expensive treatment.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:-15px; margin-right:-15px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">As the amount required is huge, I request you to kindly contribute towards the treatment and help during this time of need. Without this treatment, cancer will take her life and every single fight my child puts up against cancer will go in vain. I appeal to you to send your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of </span></span><strong>Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</strong></span></p>\r\n', '1', '2022-11-29 18:02:58'),
(44, 'Help-Aditya-win-the-deadly-battle-against-cancer!20220910122604_2.jpg', '350000', '650000', 'Help Aditya win the deadly battle against cancer!', 'Support Aditya\'s fight for survival by giving him a second chance!', '<p style=\"margin-left:-15px; margin-right:-15px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Sandeep Chungade has been working as a daily wage farmer. His life turned upside down when he got to know his child Aditya, who is just 6 years old has a life threatening cancer. As a result of his cancer, he cannot go to school, which has greatly impacted his childhood as well.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:-15px; margin-right:-15px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">At the MGM hospital in Aurangabad, child Aditya was diagnosed with T-cell Acute Lymphoblastic Leukaemia and since that day, their life has never been the same. The expenses are huge, and his family has already put everything at risk to save their little child, but now they have no resources to pay for his life-threatening, expensive treatment.&nbsp; It is a long-term treatment that is expected to cost Rs. 6,50,000/-</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:-15px; margin-right:-15px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Please consider contributing to the treatment and help during this time of need, as the amount required is large. Without this treatment, cancer will take a child&#39;s life and every single fight a child has put up against cancer will go in vain. Please send your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1', '2022-11-29 18:12:40'),
(45, 'Help-Swaranjali-relieve-from-this-unbearable-pain.20221008054807.jpg', '250000', '650000', 'Battling cancer  Swaranjali’s only hope is chemotherapy.', 'Help Swaranjali relieve from this unbearable pain.', '<p><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Swaranjali Sundar Kamble is only 8 years old and suffering from Non-Hodgkin&#39;s lymphoma (Blood Cancer) at such a young age. She is being admitted to the Mahatma Gandhi Cancer Hospital and Research Institute, Aurangabad. Doctors informed that she needed to undergo chemotherapy. The period of her treatment is 1 year and the approximate cost for the procedure is Rs. 6,50,000/-.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">Swaranjali and her family belong to Pathari town in Parbhani District in Maharashtra, and her parents work as daily wage earners. It&#39;s not been easy for them to deal with everything their daughter is going through, and their financial situation has made it difficult to provide her with treatments.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:#252525\">As parents, they were planning for her bright future until this unfortunate illness struck her life. Her family has already put everything at risk to save their little daughter. Whatever little money they had till now went into ongoing medications. Swaranjali has been a warrior so far, but she needs your help to battle this life-threatening cancer. Please send your contribution by cheque/DD/online in the name of Kokan Kala Va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha.</span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1', '2022-11-29 18:18:54');
