ing to Assam State Disaster Management Authority (ASDMA) officials, the new deaths on Sunday were reported from Nagaon (4), Cachar and Hojai districts. Of the 24 total deaths, five lost their lives in different landslide events, and 7.19 lakh lives were affected. Our team is preparing to provide urgent support to affected families. As per the current situation, food, water, and medical assistance are the ultimate needs of the hour.						</div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-90c24f0 elementor-align-left elementor-mobile-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"90c24f0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\r\n  <a href=\"../donation\" class=\"elementor-button-link elementor-button elementor-size-sm\" role=\"button\">\r\n  <span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\r\n  <span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Donate Now</span>\r\n  </span>\r\n  </a>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </section>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </section>\r\n  <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ac46982 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"ac46982\" data-element_type=\"section\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-14d20e2\" data-id=\"14d20e2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n  <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-5d190bb elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"5d190bb\" data-element_type=\"section\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-3d6d516\" data-id=\"3d6d516\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1014d82  elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1014d82\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{\"_animation\":\"fadeInDown\"}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n  <h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Disaster Preparedness</h2>		</div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-242694d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"242694d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-container parass\">\r\n  Around 85% of India’s territory is vulnerable to natural disasters, and marginalised communities, especially children are most affected. Our disaster preparedness plan aims to reduce vulnerability and build community-level resilience by developing strategies that are truly effective in protecting lives and livelihoods. We work at the grassroots level with communities and local organisations, so we can better respond to local priorities and build on local capabilities.						</div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-752626b  elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"752626b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{\"_animation\":\"zoomIn\"}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n				<img width=\"1020\" height=\"598\" src=\"../public/website/images/features.png\" class=\"attachment-2048x2048 size-2048x2048\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"../public/website/images/features.png 1020w, ../public/website/images/features-300x176.png 300w, ../public/website/images/features-768x450.png 768w, ../public/website/images/features-370x216.png 370w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px\" />															</div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-54568ac elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"54568ac\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n  <h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Around 85% of India\'s territory is vulnerable to natural disasters, and marginalised communities especially children, are most affected.</h2>		</div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </section>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  </section>\r\n  <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9454295 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"9454295\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{\"background_background\":\"classic\"}\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-32a31df\" data-id=\"32a31df\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n  <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-bc02483 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"bc02483\" data-element_type=\"section\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-a95e2c7\" data-id=\"a95e2c7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4e384cf  elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4e384cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{\"_animation\":\"fadeInDown\"}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n  <h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default parass\">Working at grassroots level, working for the welfare of people!</h2>		</div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-58050d3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"58050d3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n  <p class=\"font-weight-bold parass\"><b class=\"text-highlight\" style=\"color: #3b2b98;\">Floods are a</b> taking the lives of more than 7 lakh individuals every year. Hectares of crops are destroyed, and thousands of people are trapped and stranded as a result of this destructive situation. All over the world, 90% of all disasters are water related. Every year, 30 million people are displaced due to sudden disasters.</p>\r\n  <p class=\"font-weight-bold\">Kokan’s disaster management initiative is mainly to work in the flood-affected localities, respond to the needs of the community and ensure that the areas are resettled, which can lead to the community re-living their lives and settling themselves into their daily routine.</p>\r\n  <p class=\"font-weight-bold parass\">During the whole process, our objective is to provide urgent access to food, health, and hygiene and resettle the affected areas.</p>						</div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a7ad6ce elementor-align-left elementor-mobi