ntor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-2b6d335\" data-id=\"2b6d335\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e032e8c  elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e032e8c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{\" _animation=\"\" :=\"\" fadeindown=\"\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n	<style>/*! elementor - v3.7.8 - 02-10-2022 */\r\n	.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}\r\n	</style>\r\n	<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">About Kokan NGO</h1>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-93abb7f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"93abb7f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n	<style>/*! elementor - v3.7.8 - 02-10-2022 */\r\n	.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#818a91;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#818a91;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}\r\n	</style>\r\n	<p class=\"para\">We started our journey in 2008, with the aim and determination to make a difference in the lives of the needy, especially the underprivileged children. We have been working in Maharashtra for more than 10 years. We currently have more than 10 projects running across 8 districts of Maharashtra, where we have been able to reach a total of 47,000 children. Through our programmes, we strengthen children’s rights and help them stay safe. Our organisation was registered on May 22nd, 2012 under the Society Act 1860 and also registered under the Bombay Public Trust Act 1950 on October 30th, 2012 at Sindhudurg, Maharashtra.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</section>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</section>\r\n	<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-f97aa37 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"f97aa37\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{\" background_background=\"\" :=\"\" classic=\"\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><br />\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ffb4298\" data-id=\"ffb4298\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{\" background_background=\"\" :=\"\" classic=\"\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n	<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-878d246 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"878d246\" data-element_type=\"section\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-0badb2a\" data-id=\"0badb2a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d46acc  elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6d46acc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{\" _animation=\"\" :=\"\" fadeinleft=\"\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n	<style>/*! elementor - v3.7.8 - 02-10-2022 */\r\n	.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}\r\n	</style>\r\n	<img width=\"1440\" height=\"960\" src=\"../public/website/images/About-us.jpg\" class=\"attachment-1536x1536 size-1536x1536\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"../public/website/images/About-us-second-image.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-ac197a4 \" data-id=\"ac197a4\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{\" animation=\"\" :=\"\" fadeinright=\"\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\" style=\"margin-top: -33px;\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15dec0b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"15dec0b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n	<p class=\"para\">We are a Section 2(15) non-profit charitable organization and our primary goal is to enable underprivileged children to achieve a better life. We believe that in today’s world, just like food, shelter, education, and health are basic necessities. Our vision is to work towards creating a world where all children, regardless of their age, gender, race, color, caste, religion, origin, and physical, mental, or financial ability, will have a fair chance to get a better education and good health. We strongly believe that transparency is critical in running such an organization. Therefore, we share any and all relevant information on our website and social media pages on a regular basis. We keep our administrative expenses to a minimum and keep clear records of all our financial transactions.</p>\r\n	<p class=\"para\">Kokan Kala va Shikshan Vikas Sanstha was established in 2010 mainly to help society live better through educational and medical facilities. The organisation helps underprivileged children and promotes education, village development, support for orphanages, disaster relief support and medical support for children with severe illnesses. Having access to national associations of expertise and a wide network of partnerships enables us to deliver broad-based outcomes to a variety of stakeholders. Together, we believe that we can reach more people through education and health facilities to improve the lives of those in need.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f00ee79 elementor-mobile-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"f00ee79\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n	<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\r\n	<a href=\"../public/website/images/06/Website-file_compressed-1.pdf\" class=\"elementor-button-link elementor-button elementor-size-sm\" role=\"button\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n	<span class=\"elementor-but