ass=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n      <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-e33d9a0 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"e33d9a0\" data-element_type=\"section\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-2b6d335\" data-id=\"2b6d335\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e032e8c  elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e032e8c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{\" _animation=\"\" :=\"\" fadeindown=\"\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n      <style>/*! elementor - v3.7.8 - 02-10-2022 */\r\n      .elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}</style>\r\n      <h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">About Us</h1>\r\n      </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-93abb7f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"93abb7f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n      <style>/*! elementor - v3.7.8 - 02-10-2022 */\r\n      .elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#818a91;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#818a91;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}</style>\r\n      <p class=\"parass\">We initiated the ShriLochan Child Development Centre keeping the current state of the COVID-Pandemic in mind. How it has affected many of the commoners\' lives is unclear. It makes it more difficult for the children living on the streets without a roof over their heads. According to statistics in India today, over 9300 children lost their parents or were abandoned by their parents. It not only affects the physical health of children due to a lack of food, but it also hampers their mental health, which can lead them to several detrimental acts. Thus, taking tiny steps, we created a nature-friendly environment for kids at ShriLochan Titwala East. At present, we have 36 children who have faced difficulties at an early age and are now under the shelter of ShriLochan, where their basic needs are fulfilled. Similarly, we initiated ShriLochan in Pune.</p>\r\n      <p class=\"parass\">ShriLochan is not just an orphanage, but a home for many. These little ones are not only safe but also enjoy their childhood and live life to the fullest. In the same manner, at the ShriLochan Child Development Centre in Pune, we have 15 children and it has a capacity of 35 plus children, to accommodate and secure their future without any burden on their heads.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n      </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"9009\" class=\"elementor elementor-9009\">\r\n      <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-850467f elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"850467f\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{\" background_background=\"\" :=\"\" classic=\"\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-bdd174c\" data-id=\"bdd174c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n      <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-a106832 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"a106832\" data-element_type=\"section\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-1ae5d46 \" data-id=\"1ae5d46\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{\" background_background=\"\" classic=\"\" animation=\"\" :=\"\" zoomin=\"\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n      <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5e54bcc elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"5e54bcc\" data-eleme