ding-title elementor-size-default\" style=\"text-align: left\">Connecting them to rehabilitation centres\r\n                                    </h2>\r\n                                   </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5bda9d0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5bda9d0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n                                   <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n                                      <p>Most of the time, families of children are alcoholic and drug addicts. As part of the parental guide program, we educate them on the consequences of addiction and help them connect with rehabilitation centres.\r\n \r\n                                    </p>\r\n                                   </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                               \r\n                             </div>\r\n                          </div>\r\n                       </div>\r\n                    </section>\r\n                 </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n           </div>\r\n           <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n              <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5b7625a\" data-id=\"5b7625a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n                 <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n                    <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-5373389 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"5373389\" data-element_type=\"section\">\r\n                       <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-wider\">\r\n                          <div cla