n><span class=\"zw-portion\" data-text-len=\"5\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"zw-portion\" data-text-len=\"6\">2000/-</span><span class=\"EOP EOP-readonly\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"zw-paragraph heading4055750\" data-width=\"601\" data-header=\"4055750\" data-textformat=\"{\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-div\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-content\"><span class=\"zw-portion\" data-text-len=\"4\">Gudi</span><span class=\"zw-portion\" data-text-len=\"1\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"zw-portion\" data-text-len=\"5\">Padwa</span><span class=\"zw-portion\" data-text-len=\"52\">,&nbsp;the&nbsp;New&nbsp;Year,&nbsp;brings&nbsp;a&nbsp;new&nbsp;ray&nbsp;of&nbsp;happiness&nbsp;to&nbsp;the</span><span class=\"zw-portion\" data-text-len=\"1\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-div\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-content\"><span class=\"zw-portion\" data-text-len=\"25\">neglected&nbsp;ones&nbsp;around&nbsp;us.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Celebrating Gudi Padwa with homeless, street kids', 'Festival', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Mumbai & Pune', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3772.071109009927!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671543091753!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-10-12 13:41:52'),
(4, 'Lets Brighten a Needy Life this Diwali', 'Lets-Brighten-a-Needy-Life-this-Diwali20211029025552.webp', '2022-10-24', '', '', '<p>Diwali is coming, and our planning and preparations might have already started!</p>\r\n<p>We do celebrate Diwali and other festivals the traditional way, but have you ever felt like doing something unique, special, satisfying, just something more? To feel the joy and share it with others?</p>\r\n<p>If yes, then let&rsquo;s celebrate this Diwali with less Privileged children.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We cannot imagine Diwali without fireworks, sweets, and food. Diwali is the most sought-out festival with social and religious significance. We all wear new clothes, eat sweets, burst crackers, and light up our houses with &ldquo;in&ndash;fashion&rdquo; LED lights, candles, and traditional ideas. But ironically these things are limited for a few. The underprivileged section of our society is deprived of such things. The meaning of Diwali, its significance, rituals, and the reason why it is celebrated is beyond counting.</p>\r\n<p>Imagine yourself walking to the market in new clothes on Diwali and you see two little kids by the side of the road, sitting with torn rags asking for food or money. If we have got more than we need, so can&rsquo;t we spare some of it for the needy? A small gesture will bring smiles to their faces; a small initiative might just brighten their lives!</p>', 'Celebration of Diwali with Orphans & Needy', 'festivals in october 2022', 'Kokan Ngo', 'India', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d15133.836104560545!2d73.83614817893677!3d18.508147698658252!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3bc2c07392d7f7bb%3A0xdcfa9c4049b35081!2sSadashiv%20Peth%2C%20Pune%2C%20Maharashtra!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1672747192476!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-10-12 13:44:24'),
(5, 'Gully School', 'Gully-School20210311125807.webp', '2022-06-01', '', '', '<p>Gully school is an innovative concept initiated by Kokan Ngo; it aims towards providing mainstream education to the children living on the streets through activities. To terminate begging from children&rsquo;s lives. To provide primary and secondary education to underprivileged children by friendly education. To bring weak and deprived children in mainstream education. To develop cognitive skills of children through social participation.</p>', 'Road of Hope', 'Festivals', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Swargate, Pune', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3772.071109009927!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671543091753!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-10-12 13:46:53'),
(6, 'Christmas Presents for Orphans', 'Christmas-Presents-for-Orphans20210128044612.webp', '2022-12-25', '', '', '<p class=\"mt-0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We all possess something to give. With a personal commitment to bringing about a difference in the lives of people, you CAN make a big difference.</p>\r\n<p class=\"mt-5\">There may be Orphans, Street Children or Homeless people waiting with anxiety for a helping hand. Can a human heart ignore this and walk away?</p>\r\n<p><strong>Look around and be a Santa Claus this Christmas.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Every year on the occasion of Christmas, Santa Claus comes to give gift and chocolates to the children. While celebrating this festival most of the parent&rsquo;s (play the role of Santa Claus) gives gifts to their kids but have you thought that what happens with the orphans and street children&rsquo;s? Who will be giving gifts to them? Who will make them happy?</p>\r\n<p><strong>Let all of us initiate and celebrate Christmas in different way.</strong></p>\r\n<p>This year our organization is planning to be the Santa Claus for those who\'s parent\'s can\'t afford to be the Santa Claus or they are orphan.</p>\r\n<p><strong>You also can be the Santa Claus to make these orphans happy this year.</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Support for buying cakes, cookies, chocolates, biscuits, toys, Santa caps, Christmas tree, balloons etc. for 15 children &ndash; ?&nbsp;4500/-</li>\r\n<li>Support for buying ration Kit for (10 BPL children x ?&nbsp;700/-) - ?&nbsp;7000/-</li>\r\n<li>Support blankets &amp; Sweets to 10 street children 850 each - ?&nbsp;8500/-</li>\r\n<li>Support for buying new clothes for 5 underprivileged children ?&nbsp;2000/- each- ?&nbsp;10000/-</li>\r\n<li>Donation Amount of your choice.</li>\r\n</ol>', 'Christmas', 'Festivals', 'Kokan NGO', 'Maharashtra', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3772.071109009927!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671543091753!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-10-12 13:48:41'),
(9, 'A IMPROVE RURAL CHILDREN LEARNING INTEREST', 'IMPROVE-RURAL-STUDENT-LEARNING-INTEREST20210918123837.webp', '2021-09-23', '', '', '<p>Yuva Kiran&nbsp;is a program aimed at strengthening government educational systems and institutions. Under this program, we identify meritorious graduate students with poor financial backgrounds and provide scholarships to them who in turn would share their time and knowledge in improving the standards of students at Govt. Schools.</p>\r\n<p>Along with the educational development of the children, parent awareness is also created among the parents. We make their parents understand the importance of children\'s education.</p>\r\n<p>Due to this initiative, the parents in these villages are happy as they have observed good behavior changes in the children\'s habits, academic progress as well as up gradation in their communication skills, and self-confidence.</p>', 'Give Education to 425+ Children’s in Maval, Pune', 'Educational', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Maval Tehsil, Pune', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3772.071109009927!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671543091753!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-10 16:21:26'),
(10, 'SUPPORT EMERGENCY FLOOD RELIEF', 'SUPPORT-EMERGENCY-FLOOD-RELIEF20210724034935.webp', '2021-08-15', '', '', '<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">SUPPORT EMERGENCY FLOOD RELIEF</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif;\"><br><strong>NATURE HAS TAKEN ITS TOLL AGAIN</strong><br><br><strong>What worse can it be<span class=\"gmail_default\">??</span></strong><br>Since last &nbsp;<span class=\"gmail_default\">2020</span><span class=\"gmail_default\">,</span>&nbsp;we have been badly hit by the COVID-19 pandemic crisis and now, nature has got the whole country at stake with the massive disaster<span class=\"gmail_default\">&nbsp;due</span>&nbsp;to flooding in various parts of the country<span class=\"gmail_default\">. Many</span>&nbsp;have lost their homes, properties, and lives due to land sliding and flooding.<br>Most badly affected places like Chiplun, Ratnagiri, Kolhapur, khed<span class=\"gmail_default\">,</span>&nbsp;Lonavala,</span>Pune<span class=\"gmail_default\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Palghar, Satara have witnessed the drastic face of the monsoon.<br></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"gmail_default\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"gmail_default\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">We appeal to all the helping hearts like you to please come forward and extend your valuable support toward the noble cause of flood relief to affected lives.</span></div>', 'Hundreds of people lost lives and 5 Lakh affected', 'Helping', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Ratnagiri & Sindhudurg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3772.071109009927!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671543091753!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-10 16:25:48'),
(16, 'Mother’s day celebration at ShriLochan', 'Mother’s-day-celebration-at-ShriLochan20220504015839.webp', '2022-05-08', '', '', '<p class=\"mt-0\">Event Description</p>\r\n<div class=\"zw-paragraph heading7638944\" data-width=\"601.92\" data-header=\"7638944\" data-textformat=\"{\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-div\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-content\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-paragraph heading7638944\" data-header=\"7638944\" data-textformat=\"{\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-div\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-content\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-paragraph heading7638944\" data-width=\"601.92\" data-header=\"7638944\" data-textformat=\"{\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-div\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-content\">\r\n<div class=\"zw-line-content\">\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\">It is said that, \"God could not be everywhere, so he made mothers.\" Mother&rsquo;s Day is all about love and gratitude. It is a day to celebrate the women who brought us into this world. To honour our mothers on this day, we all strive to get them the best gifts we can.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\">Have you ever wondered how children without mothers would celebrate Mother\'s Day?</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\">There are many unfortunate children living around us who are deprived of the purest form of love, a mother&rsquo;s love. There was a time when they lost their world and lacked purpose, guidance and advocacy in life. A child who loses a parent suffers sorrow and anxiety. <strong>Mother\'s Day for our kids is no longer about the woman who brought them to life, but rather about the woman who taught them to live. </strong>Although they are cared for and nurtured at ShriLochan, there is no love that is as pure, unconditional and as strong as a mother\'s love. Our children sometimes do look for their mothers with hope in their eyes, and we request you to be that ray of hope at least for a day.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This Sunday, May 8th 2022, celebrate Mother\'s Day at our ShriLochan with children. We truly believe that the definition of motherhood doesn\'t require being a mother. We invite you to celebrate this Mother\'s Day in the true sense of the word by dedicating it to our little angels who yearn for motherly warmth.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Mother’s day celebration at ShriLochan', 'Celebration', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Mumbai & Pune', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 18:48:40'),
(17, 'Swasth Bharat, Oxy - Generation for Bharat', 'Swasth-Bharat,-Oxy---Generation-for-Bharat20210428015722.webp', '2021-04-15', '', '', '<p class=\"mt-0\">Event Description</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>With 1,82,63,695+ tested positive and with over 2,01,928 deaths (as of 27th April 2021), Coronavirus / COVID-19 has hit each of us in different forms impacting travel, business, happiness, and more than anything else - our lives.&nbsp; Oxygen is critically required to treat patients affected with COVID, many of whom require hospitalization due to fluctuating oxygen levels. However, there is a severe shortage of oxygen availability across hospitals in India. Oxygen concentrators are alternate devices to oxygen cylinders &ndash; while cylinders contain a finite amount of oxygen supply, a concentrator recycles oxygen from the air and delivers it to the patient. They can be used to manage patient requirements without looking for external sources of oxygen.</p>\r\n<p>India is waking up to the fact that there is not enough supply of oxygen to the patients who actually need it. Hospitals are not able to take any new admissions. People are waiting outside the hospitals desperately waiting for some support. There have been many deaths outside the hospitals, waiting for oxygen. Though there have been many NGOs, organizations, and The government trying their best to procure and provide the oxygen to the neediest, there is still a shortage.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It is very crucial now that we, individuals have to step in to support this crisis situation and co-operate with each other with utmost responsibility.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Each high flow oxygen concentrator costs Rs. 85,000 and each low flow concentrator costs Rs 45,000.</p>\r\n<p>A contribution of Rs.45000 will procure one low-flow concentrator that can treat and save the lives of up to 900 patients with mild to moderate illness. A contribution of Rs. 85000 will procure one high-flow concentrator that can treat and save the lives of up to 550 patients with a severe or critical illness.</p>', 'Support Needy to procure Oxygen concentrators', 'Helping', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Mumbai', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 18:54:20'),
(18, 'Old Cloth & Toys Distribution Drive', 'Old-Cloth-&-Toys-Distribution-Drive-20210311125004.webp', '2021-05-01', '', '', '<p class=\"mt-0\">Event Description</p>\r\n<p>Kokan Sanstha is a ngo that works for street children in Mumbai &amp; Pune. Kids are always in need of clothes and food, but it&rsquo;s also fun to see the expression on their faces when they are given old cloth that they can wear. Apart from this, you can also donate toys, since they love playing in groups.</p>\r\n<p>We found that kids are not having enough clothes to cover their body, also the clothes they are using are not at all help them to keep them in a good state of hygiene.</p>\r\n<p>This group is made for getting old clothes &amp; Toy Drive for such kids.</p>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>It is better to Donate, than accumulate</p>\r\n<footer class=\"border-top-0\"><cite title=\"Source Title\">Common Man</cite></footer></blockquote>\r\n</div>', 'Reusable Old Cloth Donation Drive', 'Helping', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Swargate, Pune', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 18:56:19'),
(20, 'WOMENS CARE SANITARY NAPKINS', 'WOMENS-CARE-SANITARY-NAPKINS20210303120219.webp', '2021-04-08', '', '', '<p class=\"mt-0\">Event Description</p>\r\n<p>Kokan Ngo every year Celebrates Women\'s day with tribal women as well as students of the rural area. This time also we will distribute sanitary napkins to 1000+ tribal &amp; rural women and girls in Karjat Kasara, Pune area.</p>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>You can send women\'s to the moon or mars later, first provide sanitary pads to them</p>\r\n<footer class=\"border-top-0\"><cite title=\"Source Title\">Arunachalam Murugantham - Pad Man</cite></footer></blockquote>\r\n</div>', 'Womens Day Celebration', 'Helping', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Mumbai, Thane & Pune', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 19:13:48'),
(21, 'Be the Valentine for Unloved', 'Be-the-valentine-for-unloved-20210131074551.webp', '2021-02-14', '', '', '<p class=\"mt-0\">Event Description</p>\r\n<p>It will be the best valentine if we could celebrate it with the underprivileged and or orphans. So they could know they are indeed loved by society. Our little bit of good &amp; will make a world of difference to the children in underprivileged and there\'s great joy in seeing them prosper.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Valentine is a treat for the person who we love and care for. We spent money to buy gifts, clothes, roses, etc. on this day for our loved ones. All of these children deserve the same love. Let&rsquo;s do something a little different this year.</p>\r\n<p>These children need us to do more then a little for them. Their hope is in God, and God has given us the opportunity to work for them. God is opening hearts around the world so these children will know they are not alone but loved</p>\r\n<p>We can make this day an extreme pleasure for them and it will be the best valentine&rsquo;s day of their life</p>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>&ldquo;The hunger for love is much more difficult to remove than the hunger for bread&rdquo;&hellip;..</p>\r\n<footer class=\"border-top-0\"><cite title=\"Source Title\">Mother Teresa</cite></footer></blockquote>\r\n</div>', 'Valentines day Celebration with needy Children', 'Celebration', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Mumbai', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 19:16:21'),
(22, 'Donate the Warmth', 'Donate-the-Warmth20201230074023.webp', '2021-01-26', '', '', '<p class=\"mt-0\">Event Description</p>\r\n<p><strong>While many of us enjoy the warmth of blankets in winter, there are many who are homeless shivering in the cold.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Besides the Education Support Program, Medical support program, Livelihood program &amp; skill development program, Kokan Ngo do the blanket and clothes distribution to the people who reside roadside and orphans. As a part of the Christmas Occasion event, this year we have arranges for the distribution of clothes and blankets to the street children. Till now we have distributed gifts and toys in Vai, Mahabaleshwar; in the 2nd event, we have distributed blankets to 35+ roadside poor and needy people near Swargate Pune. On 27th Dec we have distributed clothes to the 113 poor and needy street children&rsquo;s in the Dadar &amp; Wadala Area of Mumbai.&nbsp; As you can see from the photos on our website, many of the children attending our programs hardly have any clothes to wear.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We protect ourselves with warm cozy clothes in winter, while it\'s not so for little children on streets and slums, it\'s a&nbsp; misery. The homeless, especially, children suffer through bitter cold and even die.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Let\'s come together and give warmth and protection to the anxious hearts on streets and slums, from this scourging cold.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Aims &amp; Objectives:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The project sought to achieve the following objectives:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To reduce the suffering of orphans due to the cold wave.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To reduce cold-related sufferings of old women and men of extremely poor families.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To attain blessings through serving suffering humanity.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you would like to sponsor the distribution of free clothes and blankets for these poor children &amp; orphans. Please use&nbsp;<strong>UPI:kokanngo@hdfcbank</strong></p>', 'Homeless Battle Against Winter', 'Donation', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Mumbai', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 19:19:11'),
(23, 'Food for Homeless', 'Food4Homeless20200413084002.webp', '2020-05-03', '', '', '<p class=\"mt-0\">Event Description</p>\r\n<p><strong>Food for Homeless</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>LOCKDOWN IS NOT JUST A WORD TO THE PEOPLE LIVING ON THE STREETS BUT ITS THE END OF THEIR SURVIVAL</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The corona lockdown has not only resulted in losing the jobs of the daily wage earners but it has brought hunger and disparity to him and his family even to find the basic food to keep them alive.</p>\r\n<p>In this critical time, Kokan ngo is planning to stock them with 15 days of grocery requirements (repeating the cycle if the lockdown continues)</p>\r\n<p>The cost of 1 family (average 4 members) grocery comes up to Rs. 850 which includes Rice, Dal, Soap &amp; Biscuits packet.&nbsp; Currently, we have reached 1211 Families of Maharashtra &amp; Goa and our Target is to support at least 3000 Families across India.</p>\r\n<p>You can also help us by sponsoring family/families or providing the grocery in quantity for distribution.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Your small contribution will feed a family, Help them to Fight Corona</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The entire process will be in a quarantine way adhering to the rules laid by the government and no mass collection or mass distribution will take place.</p>\r\n<p>You can use UPI : kokanngo@hdfcbank</p>', 'Supplying Grocery to 3000 Needy, Homeless families', 'Helping', 'Kokan Ngo', 'Mumbai', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 19:21:29'),
(24, 'Sanitary Napkins Distribution', 'Sanitary-Napkins-Distribution20200319111826.webp', '2020-03-08', '', '', '<section>\r\n<p>Pads Should not be a Choice, It should be a right for Womens</p>\r\n<blockquote><footer class=\"border-top-0\"><cite title=\"Source Title\">Unknown</cite></footer></blockquote>\r\n</section>\r\n<footer id=\"footer\" class=\"footer pb-0 lazy\">\r\n<div class=\"container pb-20\">\r\n<div class=\"row multi-row-clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-3\">\r\n<div class=\"widget\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</footer>', 'Women\'s Day Celebration with sanitary Napkin\'s', 'Distribution', 'Sanitary Napkins to Tribal and Needy Womens', 'Kasara, Thane', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 19:23:56'),
(25, 'Support Emergency!', 'Support-Emergency!20200320070300.webp', '2020-04-15', '', '', '<p class=\"mt-0\">Event Description</p>\r\n<p>The World Health Organization has declared the coronavirus a pandemic, and the number of cases continues to rise worldwide. These basic steps can help you reduce your risk of getting sick or infecting others.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Here&rsquo;s what you can do:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Stay home if you can.</p>\r\n<p>Wash your hands. With soap. Then wash them again.</p>\r\n<p>Stay informed.</p>\r\n<p>With children, keep calm, carry on and get the flu shot.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>Say no to Panic,Say Yes to Precaution</p>\r\n<footer class=\"border-top-0\"><cite title=\"Source Title\">PM: Narendra Modi</cite></footer></blockquote>\r\n</div>', 'Support to Save Needy People from Corona', 'Support Emergency', 'Free Sanitizer & Mask in Rural & Tribal Areas', 'Mumbai', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 19:27:10'),
(26, 'Donate a Blanket, Save a life', 'Donate-a-Blanket,-Save-a-life20200117064338.webp', '2020-01-26', '', '', '<p class=\"mt-0\">Event Description</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">We all possess something to give. With a personal commitment to bringing about a difference in the lives of people, you CAN make a big difference. There may be a shivering child, an old woman or a man in your neighborhood dreading the everyday drip in temperature and waiting with anxiety for a helping hand. Can a human heart ignore this and walk away? Look around and be a hero this winter for a homeless/Orphans.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Every winter, our organization, Kokan Ngo runs Blanket Donation Campaign, where we provide high-quality warm blankets to the underprivileged, orphans and communities living in on the streets. We try our best to reach out to people in Mumbai, Thane and other parts of Maharashtra.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">There is no better gift than providing warm clothing to the needy during the winter season. Lakh of homeless and needy experience bitterness of winter and are at great risk of suffering from severe illnesses. The rise in air pollution levels and the early onset of winter this year have made them vulnerable, but at the same time, it has given us an opportunity to serve humanity by donating blankets to the needy. This winter, become a part of our mission. There cannot be a bigger satisfaction than saving someone&rsquo;s life.</p>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>Be a hero for homeless/Orphans</p>\r\n<footer class=\"border-top-0\"><cite title=\"Source Title\">Common Man</cite></footer></blockquote>\r\n</div>', 'Blanket Donation for Homeless', 'Donation', 'Donate a Blanket, Save a life', 'Mumbai', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 19:29:33'),
(28, 'Tata Mumbai Marathon', 'Tata-Mumbai-Marathon20200114082008.webp', '2020-01-19', '', '', '<p>Kokan Ngo Team is Participating in this event with the aim of motivating Runner to complete their run and to spread awareness on Girl child, Farmer Suicide, Tribal Education. it is a movement of Awareness and wants you to be a part of our team.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Let us together make a change in needy Comunity.</p>', 'Run for Supporting Girl Child', 'Marathon', 'Tata Mumbai Marathon', 'Mumbai', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 19:49:45'),
(29, 'Skill Development Course', 'Skill-Development-Course-20200104031818.webp', '2020-10-01', '', '', '<p>Education is the Movement from Darkness to light</p>\r\n<footer class=\"border-top-0\"><cite title=\"Source Title\">-Mahatma Gandhi</cite></footer>', 'Tailoring Class', 'Skill development', 'Skill Development Course', 'Shahapur', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7544.142218019854!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671801478006!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2022-12-23 19:52:10'),
(35, 'School Kit Distribution', 'Event-Title-120191117122154.webp', '1919-08-08', '', '', '<p>Education is the Movement from Darkness to light</p>\r\n<p class=\"border-top-0\"><cite title=\"Source Title\">Allan Bloom</cite></p>', 'Education Support Program', 'Distribution', 'School Kit Distribution', 'Sindhudurga', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3772.071109009927!2d72.843661!3d19.016588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x854d42a509b8d7fd!2sKokan%20Kala%20Va%20Shikshan%20Vikas%20Sanstha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671543091753!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2023-01-03 12:01:14'),
(37, 'Basic Tailoring Course', 'Basic-Tailoring-Course20191116121651 (2).webp', '2019-11-26', '', '', '<p>Activity Which gives employment to the women.</p>\r\n<p>We have currently started our new Tailoring Classes at Chunabhatti, Sion, Mumbai</p>\r\n<p>Concept behind this classes are to empower the women through training &amp; providing work to earn something for their family.</p>\r\n<p>We are planing to provide them sewing machines for free of cost so that they can start earning. Currently we have 4 machines at our class.</p>\r\n<p>We are appealing donor to use Donate Option for this cause. Cost Per machine is&nbsp;Rs.6800/-</p>\r\n<p>We need at least 30 machines.</p>', 'Basic Tailoring Course', 'Course', 'Basic Tailoring Course', 'Mumbai', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d241316.6433234205!2d72.74109800466292!3d19.082522323469465!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3be7c6306644edc1%3A0x5da4ed8f8d648c69!2sMumbai%2C%20Maharashtra!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1671541829269!5m2!1sen!2sin', '2023-01-03 12:26:21');
